@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-5">
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="6000">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1" ></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2" ></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                    <img src="~/images/MiyopRobot.jpg" alt="Miyop Robot"  width="100%" height="auto" class="img-responsive" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                        <p>
                            <a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.minepla.net">
                                Learn More
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/MiyopRobot_1.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Camera">
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/MiyopRobot_2.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="LEGO pieces">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-7">
        <div style="padding:10px 0px 0px 10px">
            <h2>What is this?</h2>
            <p> 
            This is a simple ASP.NET Core application to do some actions with <b>"Miyop Robot"</b>.
            "Miyop Robot" is a simple IoT device and also a kind of robot which runs on Raspberry Pi. The robot aspect of Miyop Robot is created with BrickPi and LEGO Mindstorms.
            All robot aspect can be extended with some other LEGO pieces. 
            </p>
            <p>
            The main purpose of "Miyop Robot" is to learn some new technologic views such as .NET Core, IoT, Raspberry Pi, python, cloud platforms, AI, Machine Learning, etc... 
            So feel free to do anything you want, to learn new things. 
            </p>
            <p>
            This web application is done with ASP.NET Core and it is running on Raspberry Pi. There are also some python scripts to do some extra jobs like executing LEGO Mindstorms' motors and getting some info about sensors. 
            This ASP.NET Core application can execute these python scripts and processes their results. "Miyop Robot" has also some features releated with cloud platforms like Microsoft Azure and Google Cloud.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

